    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "summary_evidence_body",
      "x": 870,
      "y": 500,
      "width": 540,
      "height": 92,
      "text": "1. Browser POST /api/invoke  {query, session_id}\n2. Next.js proxy normalizes slash commands, forwards to FastAPI\n3. POST /api/chat/stream → cognito_auth → load history from DynamoDB\n4. stream_generator() → sdk_query_streaming() → Strands Agent\n5. Supervisor delegates to specialist @tool subagents via Bedrock\n6. Text/tool chunks → MultiAgentStreamWriter → SSE events\n7. TransformStream pipes SSE back through proxy to browser",
      "originalText": "1. Browser POST /api/invoke  {query, session_id}\n2. Next.js proxy normalizes slash commands, forwards to FastAPI\n3. POST /api/chat/stream → cognito_auth → load history from DynamoDB\n4. stream_generator() → sdk_query_streaming() → Strands Agent\n5. Supervisor delegates to specialist @tool subagents via Bedrock\n6. Text/tool chunks → MultiAgentStreamWriter → SSE events\n7. TransformStream pipes SSE back through proxy to browser",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#22c55e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
